Description: Animated objects have a number of Construction Points (CP) used to purchase abilities and defenses in addition to those presented above. A small animated object has 1 CP; differently sized objects have CP totals as detailed on the size chart on this page. If an animated object spends more CP than its size category would allow, its CR increases by 1 (minimum of +1) for every 2 additional CP spent.
